      "content": "it felt really intense though, like i've never felt anything like it. i'm also feeling a bit dizzy and my neck feels kind of stiff. i'm pretty sure i'm just super stressed with finals and haven't been eating right. i really don't want to go to the hospital if i don't have to, it's expensive and i have so much work to do. is there anything i can take right now just to make the fog/stiffness go away so i can keep studying? maybe some ibuprofen or something stronger?",
